# 副簽
(pos:動詞/名詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺文件、證書或者簽名旁邊，由另一個人簽名以作證明或擔保（量詞：個）
eng:counter-signature; to counter-sign
<eg>
yue:呢份合約除咗老闆簽名，仲需要財務部經理副簽先至生效。 (ni5 fan6 gung3 wa3 ceoi1 zo2 lou5 baau2 sin1 ming4, zung6 seoi1 jiu3 caat4 mou6 bou6 gei2 liu5 fu3 sin1 sin1 zi1 sing1 fo3.)
eng:This contract needs the finance manager's counter-signature in addition to the boss's signature to take effect. [end of text]


